### Finance Dashboard API Tests

# --------------------------------------------------------
# 1. Healthcheck
# --------------------------------------------------------
GET http://localhost:3000/health

###

# --------------------------------------------------------
# 2. Authentication (Register an Admin)
# --------------------------------------------------------
# @name registerAdmin
POST http://localhost:3000/api/v1/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@finance.com",
  "password": "securepassword123",
  "name": "Admin User",
  "role": "ADMIN"
}

###

# --------------------------------------------------------
# 3. Authentication (Login)
# Extract the token from the response for the next steps!
# --------------------------------------------------------
# @name login
POST http://localhost:3000/api/v1/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@finance.com",
  "password": "securepassword123"
}

###

# --------------------------------------------------------
# Set your token here after logging in
# --------------------------------------------------------
@token = REPLACE_WITH_YOUR_COPIED_TOKEN_HERE

# --------------------------------------------------------
# 4. Create a Financial Record (Admin only)
# --------------------------------------------------------
POST http://localhost:3000/api/v1/records
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "amount": 2500,
  "type": "INCOME",
  "category": "Salary",
  "date": "2026-04-01T10:00:00Z",
  "notes": "April Salary"
}

###

# --------------------------------------------------------
# 5. Get Dashboard Summary (Available to all authenticated roles)
# --------------------------------------------------------
GET http://localhost:3000/api/v1/dashboard/summary
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

# --------------------------------------------------------
# 6. List Records
# --------------------------------------------------------
GET http://localhost:3000/api/v1/records
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
